original_title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Deer Huntin'
overview: This is the first video featuring the red neck hunting duo on a mission to bag the elusive buck known as "Split Toe".  The hunters use their expertise and knowledge of the Alabama backwoods to track the trophy deer.
tagline: Sit back and relax, as we learn y'all how to grunt-up a big-un.
title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Deer Huntin'
